### Set this value high enough<ul><li>If you detect too much oversegmentation (false bonds) then increase this value</li><li>If you start to lose too many cell contacts then decrease this value</li></ul>

### Set this value as low as possible<ul><li>If individual contacts become wiggly do increase this value</li></ul>
